detail.name: Zen-Oh
detail.effect: [On Play] Choose all cards in the Battle Areas other than this card and place them at the bottom of their owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: 全王
detail.effect: 【登場時】このカード以外のバトルエリアのカードすべてを選び、ランダムな順番で持ち主のデッキの下に置く。

faq.question: When this card is played, do you also have to choose your Battle Cards and [Field] Extras for this card's [On Play] skill?
faq.answer: Yes. Except for this card, you must choose all cards in the Battle Areas, including your cards.

faq.question: このカードを登場させた場合、【登場時】スキルで自分のバトルカードや【フィールド】を持つエクストラも選ばなくてはいけませんか？
faq.answer: はい、自分のものを含め、このカード以外のバトルエリアのカードすべてを選ばなくてはいけません。
